headline: JFrog Appoints Seasoned CIO and Digital Transformation Executive Sigal Zarmi to its Board of Directors
summary: SUNNYVALE, Calif., September 25, 2025--JFrog Ltd. ("JFrog") (Nasdaq: FROG), the Liquid Software company and creators of the JFrog Software Supply Chain Platform, today announced Sigal Zarmi will join its Board of Directors, effective November 1, 2025.

headline: Bear Icebox Communications Named 'Campaign of the Year' Finalist for the 2025 PRNews Platinum PR Awards
summary: PRNEWS has named Bear Icebox Communications a Finalist for B2B Campaign of the Year in the 2025 Platinum PR Awards. The recognition follows a record-breaking number of entries and a rigorous review process by 200 judges, marking it as one of the industry's most competitive and meaningful honors.
